Body:
b'     Dear friends and volunteers   Greetings from the NSS family!  "The best way to find yourself is to lose yourself in the service of others" Mahatma Gandhi  NSSIITM continues on its mission to be at the service of humanity with a new year of activities. We commence the events and projects for the year with the Inauguration Ceremony to be conducted on  20th August 2016 , Saturday at  11:00 am  in  Central Lecture Theatre   (CLT) , IITM.   Ms Aruna Roy  has consented to be the chief guest at the function. Former IAS officer and Magsaysay award recipient, Ms Aruna Roy is an RTI activist and founder of the Mazdoor Kisan Shakti Sangathan.  We cordially invite you all to the Inaugural Ceremony.  PS:This is Credited event for all NSS Confirmed Volunteers and Defaulters.   Thanks and Regards,  Managerial team, NSS IIT Madras  Website:  www.nss.iitm.ac.in Facebook:  www.facebook.com/nss.iitm  '

